{{> header}}
<h1>Your password has been changed</h1>
<p>Hi {{name}}, this is a confirmation that the password for your Team Workspace account was successfully changed.</p>
<div class="card">
  <p><strong>Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
  <p><strong>IP address:</strong> {{ip}}</p>
</div>
<p>If you made this change, no further action is needed.</p>
<hr>
<div class="alert">
  <p>⚠️ &nbsp;<strong>Didn't change your password?</strong> Your account may be compromised. <a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="color:#92400e;font-weight:600;">Reset it immediately</a> and contact support.</p>
</div>
{{> footer}}
